Paste the Vimes installation script into your terminal
use command "vimesget" to use the tool
Example usage "vimesget New York" "vimesget London" 
use 4 different arguments
-r (for robberies)
-m (for murders)
-g (for gang crimes)
-s (for knife crime)
Example of argument use "vimesget -s London"
Example of argument use "vimesget -m Chicago"
Example of argument use "vimesget -g USA"
Example of argument use "vimesget -r France"

Vimes the fearless night watch officer will track down those criminals with his trusted watchmen Nobby and Colon
This tool will search for recent crimes that happened in the past 6 months and sort them in chronological order from distant to recent in your terminal.
